yle=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;\"></span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 1.1em; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); letter-spacing: 0.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 16px;\">第一，懂得拒绝。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 1.1em; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); letter-spacing: 0.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 16px;\">会拒接的女人是聪明的女人，她们懂得欲拒还迎，懂得分寸与进退。一个女人如果凡事都听男人的，对男人有求必应，自然在男人心中就会毫无地位。这样的女人，在男人的眼中毫无征服的价值，自然就不愿意对你太好了。花费时间在你身上干嘛？他什么都不做，你都已经那么主动了。所以聪明的女人应该学会的第一点就是拒绝。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 1.1em; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); letter-spacing: 0.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 1.1em; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); letter-spacing: 0.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"https://www.myzxx.cn/static/umeditor/upload/20181008/84502a54.jpg\" _src=\"https://www.myzxx.cn/static/umeditor/upload/20181008/84502a54.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 8px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 1.1em; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); letter-spacing: 0.6px; white-space: normal; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(89, 8